data.description: Make this one story, 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home yours today! This quaint home is located in the highly sought after Southton Meadows subdivision. Beautiful Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout. Bright, open and airy floor plan with neutral tones. Great sized rooms and closets. Enjoy making your favorite meals in the open kitchen, countertop and plenty of cabinet space are great features in this home! The backyard is perfect for entertaining with plenty of room, and a wood privacy fence. Located near major highways, schools and shopping!
